279
00:15:36,810 --> 00:15:38,609
Don't you intend to explain yourself?

280
00:15:40,090 --> 00:15:41,489
100 yuan is enough, right?

281
00:15:41,969 --> 00:15:42,769
100 yuan?

282
00:15:43,690 --> 00:15:44,729
Keep the change.

283
00:15:47,009 --> 00:15:47,849
Mr. Xiao.

284
00:15:47,849 --> 00:15:49,230
Has Lan Yao arrived?
We have an appointment.

285
