Since I'm imprisoned,

316
00:17:13,010 --> 00:17:14,169
that means

317
00:17:15,090 --> 00:17:17,050
I've gotten rid of the villain.

318
00:17:23,570 --> 00:17:25,530
God of Heaven, thank you
for your blessings.

319
00:17:25,609 --> 00:17:26,689
She must've lost her mind.

320
00:17:27,409 --> 00:17:28,169
Really?

321
00:17:29,250 --> 00:17:30,730
It shouldn't be that bad, right?

322
00:17:36,409 --> 00:17:37,290
I'm hungry.

323
00:17:37,470 --> 00:17:38,290
What about you guys?

324
00:17:42,250 --> 00:17:43,050
Prison guard.

325
00:17:49,209 --> 00:17:50,689
It's time for our last meal.

326
00:17:56,209 --> 00:17:57,050
What did you say?

327
00:17:59,689 --> 00:18:00,609
Actually,

328
00:18:02,330 --> 00:18:03,530
