334
00:18:15,530 --> 00:18:16,849
Everyone has a duty

335
00:18:16,849 --> 00:18:18,530
to maintain public security.

336
00:18:23,330 --> 00:18:24,369
She...

337
00:18:25,250 --> 00:18:28,409
She's mentally unstable.
She loves to fantasize about things.

338
00:18:29,570 --> 00:18:31,050
In order to make her recover faster,

339
00:18:31,050 --> 00:18:33,050
I have no choice but to follow
the doctor's advice

340
00:18:33,050 --> 00:18:34,330
and engage in roleplay with her.

341
00:18:34,770 --> 00:18:37,929
Coincidentally,
her illness started to act up.

342
00:18:38,129 --> 00:18:39,770
That's why this happened.

343
00:18:39,810 --> 00:18:40,730
Officer Li, I'm sorry.

344
00:18:40,730 --> 00:18:41,930
Sorry for causing you trouble.

345
00:18:43,929 --> 00:18:45,330
Young man,

346
00:18:46,570 --> 00:18:48,169
shouldn't you and your girlfriend

347
00:18:48,440 --> 00:18:50,330
draw a line even when
you two are playing games?

348
00:18:52,609 --> 00:18:53,449
Yes, sir.

349
00:18:54,090 --> 00:18:55,609
You're right.

350
00:18:56,090 --> 00:18:58,929
I'll take her home now.

351
